RWE May Seek Outside Candidate to Follow Grossmann, Spiegel Says

-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-05-15T14:26:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-15/rwe-may-seek-outside-candidate-to-follow-grossmann-spiegel-says.html
RWE AG may seek a candidate from
outside the firm to succeed Juergen Grossmann, executive board
chairman,  Der Spiegel  reported without saying where it got the
information.  Spiegel said that Lanxess AG Chairman Axel Heitmann had
conducted discussions with RWE about the position in recent
weeks.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in Frankfurt 
